# RetireSmart Canada

Personal Canadian retirement calculator. Client-side only. Not financial advice.

Canonical agent entry: root `AGENTS.md`. Domain math: `docs/explanation/math-model.md`. Doc system: `docs/README.md`.

## Architecture

- Types/enums in `src/types/calculator.ts` only. Prefer enums over string unions.
- `import type` under `verbatimModuleSyntax`.
- No third-party chart libs; custom SVG only.
- `localStorage` key `retiresmart_plan_v1` only — no backend.

## Math (summary — details in docs)

- Target backsolve + account buckets + RRIF rules; see `docs/explanation/math-model.md`.
- Do not treat all wealth as taxable RRSP; do not invent tax rules absent from that doc / ADRs.

## Testing

- Logic changes: tests in `src/test/`. Skip full runs for pure styling tweaks.
